The evidence with the title 'The estate tax isn't destroying family farms | Al Jazeera America ' says Mar 27, 2015  ... The fact is that any claim that the estate tax is killing family farms is a lie . How many of America 's 2.2 million farms have been sold to pay estate taxes? None. Committee Republicans tried to explain away that inconvenient fact by saying that the estate tax forces farmers to set aside so much money to pay it  ... 
